{"tid":2222340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大口狗：一直有信心民主派議員會留任","createTime":"2020-09-29T04:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T05:41:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15048dfbdfc4e0688ab111f90ba93a06b4b7dbd4","tid":2222340,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會主席梁君彥指，秘書長正處理陳志全及朱凱廸決定不續任議員的信件，至於其他民主派的決定，他指一直有信心議員會續任。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥：「他們的決定，我會尊重，人多一向好做事，議會需要有多些議員，有不同聲音發聲，才能做好我們的工作。（現較大機會不會有總辭？會否舒一口氣？）我一向都有信心他們會留任。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=407283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407283&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=fd2027b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407283&h=520d1189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=407283</a>"},{"pid":"d59b5cfa3c08e551827ea7c64762e5a9bc6a4600","tid":2222340,"uid":13936,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"擺明夾好哂"},{"pid":"4e3e5ffde328a1d0c5a20cc91445c3848a91cbc2","tid":2222340,"uid":316329,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"大家自己友 之後繼續齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf34c615cf8050e41e74e34ed12b8c9ecfd6cd65","tid":2222340,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe074355db00e5d108f50bf3920d539fc8be15d6","tid":2222340,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"建制狗今次係好多花生食嘅 公